  "interpretation": "Under true force-model/process-noise mismatch the visible-update innovations are dominated by an unmodelled dynamics bias, not by measurement noise. The AUKF reacts by inflating its measurement-noise diagonal (mean effective R scale > 1) and applying robust down-weighting, which shrinks the very state corrections needed to track the biased prior. EKF keeps a tighter gain and so tracks the drifting truth best; AUKF damps itself the most and is worst."
